## Kubernetes - Resource Limits

apiversion: v1
kind: pod 
metadata:
   name: pathnex-limited-pod
spec:
  containers:
    - name: app
    image: nginx
    resources:
    limits:
      memory: "256Mi"
      cpu: "500m"


# Day-05  - Environmnet Variables

## jenkins pipeline - use Environmnet Variable
 we will learn how to use ** environmnet vavriables in jenkins pipelines

 pipelines {
    agent any 
    environment {
        INSTITUTE_NAME = "Pathnex"
    } 
    stages {
        stages('Print') {
            steps {
                sh 'echo "Welcome to $INSTITUTE_NAME Devops Training"'
            }
        }
        stage('Build ') {
            steps {
                sh 'mvn clean package -Dinstitute.name=$INSTITUTE_NAME'
            }
        }
    }
 }

